response.original_title: How to Talk to Girls at Parties
response.overview: In 1970s London, a teenage outsider named Enn falls in love with a rebellious alien girl named Zan, who has come to Earth for a party. Together, they navigate the complexities of intergalactic culture and the trials of first love.
response.tagline: Some girls are out of this world
